Source: ttf-thai-siampradesh
Section: x11
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Anuchit Chalothorn <anuchit@redlinesoft.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7)
Standards-Version: 3.8.1
Homepage: http://linux.thai.net/projects/thaifonts-siampradesh

Package: ttf-thai-siampradesh
Architecture: all
Depends: defoma
Description: Thai TrueType fonts derived from DIP/SIPA contested fonts
 This package provides Thai fonts derived from winning fonts of a contest arranged by 
 Department of Intellectual Properties and Software Industry Promotion Agency, Thailand, 
 in TrueType format. It includes fonts with new original designs for use in normal texts 
 as well as decorative and hand-writing fonts. 

